    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overview</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;Spectrum of the Puddle&quot; is an exhilarating action game where water and light bounce around.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies appear on fixed 2D screens—take them down one after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game consists of a total of four stages, each filled with hordes of enemies and a boss awaiting the protagonist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist's weapon may be just an ordinary umbrella, but in the world of puddles, it’s a valiant hero’s sword. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It can even fire lasers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/extras/2c76049c2c4a36bbfa69a59b621001ea.poster.avif?t=1738116113\" width=512 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/extras/2c76049c2c4a36bbfa69a59b621001ea.webm?t=1738116113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/extras/2c76049c2c4a36bbfa69a59b621001ea.mp4?t=1738116113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game System</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to regular attacks, you can dodge danger by guarding or jumping.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features powerful &quot;skills&quot; and &quot;belongings&quot; that grant unique effects to the protagonist. You'll have opportunities to customize these during gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ストーリー</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;A mysterious world where puddles stretch on endlessly.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In the rain-washed sky, a rainbow lingered, never fading away.&quot;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lonely girl wandered into another world.<br>What will she encounter here, and what thoughts will fill her mind?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/extras/0bf112024e1093350ec55272adeb0f24.avif?t=1738116113\" width=630 height=314 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;I wonder how many colors I’d divide a rainbow into.&quot;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
